      "title": "Cancel Friday holiday",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Due to fuel issues, the special holiday granted to government employees on Fridays has been cancelled.",
        "Yesterday (01) the cabinet gave its approval to cancel the circular for granting Friday holiday."
